track_notes: If you are fit, it will take you only 45 minutes to reach the summit. There is a large meadow where the family can have a rest while your are going up this mountain; there is no path, so just climb straith north in between vegetation, after few minuts you will be able to see the summit where there is no much to set antenna but the place is large enought, beware of the sloope on north side, it is dangerous.
track_title: The shortest but not the easiest path

track_notes: First Le MONT and second Mont de Lieuche
This is a short walk to summit! There is no path and the average slope is 20%; must wear good shoes! nothing to fix antenna on summit, park is fine at the col de la Sine 1438m.
